            <p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:14px;color:var(--text-2);line-height:1.6;">85 conversations/month, 2-person team, branded chat needed. <strong>Plan: Starter ($24.17/month annual).</strong> Branding removal not yet priority. No paid Lyro yet. <strong>Real monthly cost: ~$24.</strong></p>
          </div>

          <div style="background:var(--bg-3);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:24px;margin:24px 0;">
            <p style="margin:0 0 8px 0;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--vio);letter-spacing:.1em;">// EXAMPLE C — DTC supplements, $80k/month GMV</p>
            <p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:14px;color:var(--text-2);line-height:1.6;">350 conversations/month, 4-person team, Lyro AI active for FAQ deflection, Flows for cart recovery, branding removed. <strong>Plan: Growth ($59/month monthly) + Lyro ($75/month for ~150 AI conversations) + Flows ($29/month) + branding removal ($20/month).</strong> <strong>Real monthly cost: ~$183.</strong> At this volume, Gorgias Basic ($60/month + ~$50 in overages) starts to compete on price with deeper Shopify integration.</p>
          </div>

          <p>The pattern: the advertised price covers maybe 40-50% of what the bill actually becomes. Lyro and Flows together can equal or exceed the base plan. Plan accordingly — and re-evaluate against Gorgias once you cross 200 conversations/month.</p>
