          <details style="background:var(--bg-3);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:20px 24px;">
            <summary style="cursor:pointer;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);">Is Tidio worth it for a Shopify store?</summary>
            <div style="margin-top:12px;font-size:15px;color:var(--text-2);line-height:1.65;">
              <p>Tidio is worth it for Shopify stores under $50,000/month GMV with under 200 support conversations per month, operating primarily through live chat and email, with a 1-3 person team. Below 50 conversations/month the free plan handles the workload at zero cost. Above 200 conversations or with a team of 4+ agents, ticket-based platforms like Gorgias usually have better unit economics.</p>
