          <details style="background:var(--bg-3);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:20px 24px;">
            <summary style="cursor:pointer;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);">How much does Tidio cost in 2026?</summary>
            <div style="margin-top:12px;font-size:15px;color:var(--text-2);line-height:1.65;">
              <p>Five tiers: Free ($0/month, 50 conversations, 10 seats, 50 one-time Lyro), Starter ($24.17/month annual or $29 monthly, 100 conversations), Growth ($49.17/month annual scaling to ~$349 by volume, 250+ conversations), Plus ($749/month, removes the 10-seat cap), Premium ($2,999+/month). Lyro AI is separately billed at $32.50-$39/month and scales by volume. Flows are separately billed at $24.17-$29/month per 2,000 reached visitors. Real bills typically 2-3x the advertised plan price.</p>
