            <summary style="cursor:pointer;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);">How does Lyro AI pricing work in Tidio?</summary>
            <div style="margin-top:12px;font-size:15px;color:var(--text-2);line-height:1.65;">
              <p>Lyro AI is a separate add-on billed independently. Every account gets 50 one-time Lyro conversations as a lifetime trial. Beyond that, paid Lyro starts at $32.50-$39/month for 50 AI conversations and scales to ~$289/month for higher tiers. Lyro can run independently without a paid Tidio plan at approximately $0.58 per AI conversation. Lyro replies don't count toward the base plan's billable conversation limit.</p>
