              <p>Use Tidio if your store is under $50,000/month GMV, you handle under 200 conversations per month, you have a 1-3 person team, and you operate primarily through chat and email. Use Gorgias if your store is doing $50,000+/month GMV, handling 200+ tickets across multiple channels, with a team of 3+ agents. Stores typically grow into Gorgias from Tidio, not the other way around. <a href="/blog/tidio-vs-gorgias-shopify/" style="color:var(--g);">Full comparison here.</a></p>
            </div>
