            <summary style="cursor:pointer;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);">Why did Tidio double prices in December 2024?</summary>
            <div style="margin-top:12px;font-size:15px;color:var(--text-2);line-height:1.65;">
              <p>In December 2024, Tidio implemented a major pricing change that effectively doubled bills for many existing customers (cases of $32 jumping to $64/month) without adequate advance notice. Reports describe automatic credit card charges before customers could react. This is the single biggest credibility issue with Tidio in 2026 reviews. Mitigation: stay on monthly billing for 60-90 days before considering annual, monitor announcements, and have a migration plan ready.</p>
